PERMITTED USES
===================

	- You are permitted to use MODIFIED or UNMODIFIED SlimeCraftSMP projects on any Minecraft server, public or private. It is recommended, but not required, that you give credit to SlimeCraftSMP or note somewhere on your server that said projects are in use.

	- You are permitted to use MODIFIED or UNMODIFIED SlimeCraftSMP projects for your personal endeavors such as servers, as long as the other guidelines of this License have been followed, appropriate credit has been given, and as long as you have not been specifically prohibited from doing so.

PROHIBITED USES
====================

	- You are forbidden to use any MODIFIED or UNMODIFIED SlimeCraftSMP project for "commercial use". "commercial use" describes any project/server that involves financial gain.

	- You are forbidden to reupload, republish, or redistribute any MODIFIED or UNMODIFIED SlimeCraftSMP project.

	- You are forbidden to modify any MODIFIED or UNMODIFIED SlimeCraftSMP project. There are two exceptions for this:

		i) Modifying a project for the purpose of making a contribution is allowed.
		ii) Modified projects must have the source public, changes documented and a copy of this license included with the project.

	- You are forbidden to use SlimeCraftSMP projects in their MODIFIED or UNMODIFIED form in a publicly distributed project such as a server template etc.

	- You are forbidden to use portions of any SlimeCraftSMP project's code as part of any other project without express permission. You are free to read the code and use it as a resource to learn from, but copying parts of it into another project is not allowed. There is one exception for this:

		i) Making compatibility addons between SlimeCraftSMP projects and other projects is allowed.

	- All parties (including individuals, companies, organizations and any other groups), without permission from SlimeCraftSMP, are expressly forbidden from using SlimeCraftSMP properties, textures, code, and other works, as part of a training dataset for artificial intelligence, neural networks, or other generative systems. Additionally, any and all code, textures, and all other products (digitial or physical), created and owned by SlimeCraftSMP or its members, may not be used to configure, test, debug, or augment any artificial intelligence, neural network, or other generative system.

		* This prohibition applies even if the resulting system does not store, refer to or directly call from code, textures, or other works owned by SlimeCraftSMP.

